Groan Tube Hero test guide

1. Start the game in Studio.
2. Trigger the StartPrompt on the stage.
3. Use ← → ↑ ↓ or the mobile arrow buttons to hit notes.
4. Watch the judgement text, combo, hype, stage flashes, and results screen.
5. Try store, upgrades, missions, and audience actions.
6. If audio fails to load, the rhythm gameplay still runs visually.
]]
